<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued March 27 at 3:03PM EDT until March 28 at 8:00AM EDT by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM EDT MONDAY...
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 2 to 4 inches.
Storm total snowfall amounts of 3 to 7 inches.
* WHERE...Northern Herkimer County.
* WHEN...Until 8 AM EDT Monday.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. Travel will be
difficult at times with snow covered roads and poor visibility.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.</instruction>
